results.releaseNotes: We added translations to several languages, worked on maps scaling, displaying the kid’s position in the list of children and corrected several bugs in the new version.
results.description:
Find my kids is an app for thoughtful parents. The application will give you an opportunity to see the kid’s location online, the level of his activity during the day and statistics of application using on his phone.You can also hear the sound around the kid's device and will get notifications:
- about kid’s entering / exiting from the home and other places, that you will create;
- about low charge of his phone;
- when the kid pressed a "SOS button".

To start you need to install the app on your and the kid's phone.  You can also connect a gps-watch or gadget, which are available in our store.
The application has two modes - a parent and a kid, and while only parent can use all the functions of the service, the kid’s device should definitely allow the access to all functions during the installing.

The information about kid’s location is updated every 15 minutes, but you can request gps coordinates at any time you want to, using the update function. If the kid's phone stops sending data, the app will notify you about it and will suggest possible reasons.

Supported models:
Q50, Q60, Q60s, Gw900, Gw900s, Q70, Q75, Q80, Gw100, Q90, Q100, Q200, Q360, Q1000, Q1000s, Gw100s, Gw200s, Gw300s, Gw300s, Gw400s, Gw1000, Ew100, Ew200,
Gw700, T58, Smart Pet Tracker (all possible model versions), Ew100s, Gw500s, L70, L70s, G10, G100, W8, W9, S1, D99, D100, PT01.

You can use all the functions of the app for free, within 7 days after the first launch of the application. At the end of this period  you will be able to use only the online location function in the free version.
To access all the functions of the app you need to by a subscription.

The subscription cost will be charged from your score, linked in iTunes account. Your subscription will be automatically renewed at regular intervals, according to the selected, if you don’t cancel it earlier than 24 hours before the end of the current period. You will not be able to unsubscribe after you purchase it. Subscription changes are available in Settings of your iTunes account after purchase.

Solicited access:
- to the camera and photo - to install the avatar when you register the kid
- to contacts - when you set gps-watch (select phone numbers from contacts)
- to geo-position, including the background mode - to find the kid’s location
- to the microphone - to make calls to the kid
- to push notifications - to send chat notifications

Get acquainted to the Terms of Use you can on the link below: http://findmykids.org/offer/mixed_ios.pdf  

Privacy policy: http://findmykids.org/offer/pp_mixed_ios.pdf

If you have any suggestions or questions about our application, please contact us v@lappc.ru or on our site http://findmykids.org/faq#faq
